  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pads for Girls</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will deliver 2000 menstrual kits to girls in Eastern  and Northern Uganda. One kit contains 3 regular size pads + 1 maxi pad + 1 storage bag + 1 booklet with information on menstruation. They can be reused for upto 4 years that is 100 washes. We relieve girls of the economic burdens caused by having to take care of their menstrual hygiene care during the COVID-19 pandemic by  offering a more sustainable method. We would like also to help dispel myths and taboos about menstruation.</narrative>
  </description>
